{"tid":1824944,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"「堅持呀，霞姨」","createTime":"2020-01-15T01:09:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-15T01:36:19.000Z","uid":333051,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"4fb7b5671c0a7f8fd113846955ebadca118084b3","tid":1824944,"uid":333051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T01:09:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">咁多放負posts，so what?<br />\n<br />\n話俾你地知，<br />\n我唔會理政府、藍絲、分化撚，<br />\n我會繼續每日幫襯黄店，<br />\n我會繼續有遊行集會就出席，<br />\n我會繼續有網上聯署就幫手簽，<br />\n我會繼續有眾籌就會捐款。<br />\n<br />\n憑我地水滴石穿既毅力，<br />\n我相信時間會為我地帶來希望。<br />\n<br />\n星期日見。<br />\n<br />\n<em>「你講咩姐你！」<br />\n「堅持呀，霞姨⋯⋯」<br />\n<strong>《喜劇之王》</strong></em></span>"},{"pid":"35d277f267ac372d745532e6defddc1643574814","tid":1824944,"uid":333051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T01:10:38.000Z","msg":"星期日遊行見"},{"pid":"d57508f40c2a131d21402c9a4e0aa0ba08539e83","tid":1824944,"uid":333051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T01:10:54.000Z","msg":"星期日遊行見"},{"pid":"62a4025f6ecd9061b709e362cf9942b2535cdcfb","tid":1824944,"uid":333051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T01:11:04.000Z","msg":"星期日遊行見"},{"pid":"4f0d9ba047d5e8094738661e17a36f404994caf7","tid":1824944,"uid":333051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T01:11:18.000Z","msg":"星期日遊行見"},{"pid":"b332db8a9d40eafb7c34bf5a36bd775ef4a1e98d","tid":1824944,"uid":333051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T01:11:54.000Z","msg":"星期日遊行見"},{"pid":"9a1f9e5c29221fb31f954b17233430a9aba29923","tid":1824944,"uid":333051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T01:12:06.000Z","msg":"星期日遊行見"},{"pid":"e47c676c927c3b3f507393398c9d3423f91a666e","tid":1824944,"uid":333051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T01:12:35.000Z","msg":"星期日遊行見"},{"pid":"16ddd4be32e829cd3e9aadb18a8788c99c4b2e4a","tid":1824944,"uid":3330